text: Jand Khanzada is a village and Union Council, an administrative subdivision, of Chakwal District in the Punjab Province of Pakistan, it is part of Chakwal Tehsil and is located at 32°56'0N 73°6'0E.Location of Jand Khanzada - Falling Rain Genomics The name means village of Khanzada. ==References== Category:Union councils of Chakwal District
title: Jand Khanzada
